 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Around Christmas time you can always expect an unexpected guest, so you welcome them with open arms and a glass of wine.&nbsp; That's why I decided to make a lasagne and freeze it.&nbsp; Then it's just a matter of taking it out and warming it up, with a salad and a fresh roll on the side.&nbsp; This recipe is enough for 14 people.&nbsp; If there are fewer of you, just halve it.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Lasagne is comfort food that leaves many people eating with pure contentment.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/images4.jpg\"></a></p>",
