  "ingredientsTitle": "Ingredients",
  "ingredientGroups": [
   {
    "title": null,
    "items": [
     "1 onion",
     "4 cloves garlic<br><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-002-300x225.jpg\" title=\"lasange-blog-002\" alt class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\">",
     "30 ml oil",
     "1.5 kg good mince",
     "1 tin tomato puree",
     "1 tin chopped tomato and onion mix<br><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-024-300x225.jpg\" title=\"lasange-blog-024\" alt class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\">",
     "1 tub tomato paste<br><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-026-300x225.jpg\" title=\"lasange-blog-026\" alt class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\">",
     "1 cup red wine",
     "2 cups beef stock",
     "20 ml mixed herbs",
     "salt and pepper",
     "3 sprigs thyme<br><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-015-300x225.jpg\" title=\"lasange-blog-015\" alt class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\">",
     "1 packet lasagne sheets<br><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-058-300x225.jpg\" title=\"lasange-blog-058\" alt class=\"direction-step-image\" loading=\"lazy\">"
    ]
   },
   {
    "title": "The cheese sauce",
    "items": [
     "100 ml butter<br>",
     "100 ml flour<br>",
     "salt and pepper<br>",
     "500 &#8211; 700 ml milk<br>",
     "1 tub cream cheese<br>",
     "1 1/2 cups grated cheese"
    ]
   }
  ],
  "directionsTitle": "Method",
  "directionGroups": [
   {
    "title": null,
    "steps": [
     "Chop your onion and fry in the oil until glassy.",
     "Add the garlic and fry a little longer.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-006.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt title=\"lasange-blog-006\">",
     "Stir in your mince and break it up so it doesn't clump – use a fork.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-010.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt title=\"lasange-blog-010\">",
     "Add all the rest of the ingredients (except the lasagne sheets) and now let it cook for at least 90 to 120 minutes.<br>",
     "You'll see the colour turn a deep red/brown.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-065.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt title=\"lasange-blog-065\">"
    ]
   },
   {
    "title": "For the cheese sauce",
    "steps": [
     "Melt the butter in a pot.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-041.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-041.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 041\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>",
     "Stir in the flour, salt and pepper with a whisk.",
     "Now slowly add the milk, stirring constantly until it's as thick as custard.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-048.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-048.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 048\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>",
     "Stir in the tub of cream cheese.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-054.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-054.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 054\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>",
     "Stir in 1/2 cup of the grated cheese and simmer for 5 minutes.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-056.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-056.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 056\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>"
    ]
   },
   {
    "title": "Assembling the lasagne",
    "steps": [
     "Spoon a little of the cheese sauce into the bottom of an oven dish.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-069.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-069.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 069\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>",
     "Layer lasagne sheets on top of the cheese sauce.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-073.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-073.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 073\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>",
     "Now spoon some of the meat mixture on top of the lasagne sheets.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-075.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1125\" height=\"1500\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-075.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 075\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>",
     "Repeat the layers and finish with a layer of cheese sauce. Sprinkle the remaining grated cheese on top.<br><a rel aria-label href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-080.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1500\" height=\"1125\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/lasange-blog-080.jpg\" class=\"direction-step-image\" alt=\"lasange blog 080\" title=\"Lasagne - ou staatmaker\"></a>"
    ]
   }
